(2) An initial Priority List shall be acknowledged by the collaborative not
later than one hundred eighty calendar days after the effective date of this
Subpart, following the data-driven process specified in Subsection B of this
Section, and shall be published on the publicly accessible website maintained
pursuant to R.S. 17:189.3.
(3) No Jump Start pathway shall be authorized under this Subpart unless
